>\n事實係溫溫下又走去禁下電話 睇下電話 食下零食<br />\n鳩揭下d書 照抄本書既note又唔係溫<br />\n<br />\n如果有plan既一定係要夠訓 要有休息同自由活動時間<br />\n用最少時間清concept 用最多時間操卷架啦<br />\n乜撚抗拒休息<br />\n同果班減肥撚一樣 頭一個禮拜日日跑10k 以為自己好有決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7543fcb7557cc0a4033af5e01f07ac28756aeb6d","tid":1165104,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8782380a5d94c133118cd3ddca6b2f6a96502aa7","tid":1165104,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83bfa28d4ffa04c081d3a359b703a0b744d5471","tid":1165104,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e2061f5440ebd505a957767f908f047ef6045a0","tid":1165104,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"宿舍班NDS朝八晚十咁溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"local勁個班都係痴線，exam 2個鐘可以寫14-15頁又有內容，平時8個鐘起跳。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"我之前take 一個politics course 一個鐘寫完8版就早走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走嘅時候見到有人已經寫咗12版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:16:31.000Z","msg":"之後我8版都係拎A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520a1ba32971e576f17cd3e14e7bbd84cf1941e8","tid":1165104,"uid":56661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87d3dae68d44e46a6d67453bf50542a4364b47d8","tid":1165104,"uid":132587,"like":592,"dislike":8,"score":584,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"呢四成通常都會入曬ive<br />\n成日以為自己好勤力呀唔食晏 通頂溫書就好撚搏盡無悔<br />\n事實係溫溫下又走去禁下電話 睇下電話 食下零食<br />\n